    {
      "line": 47,
      "text": "William Irwin Thompson"
    },
    {
      "line": 48,
      "text": "on the emerging Gaian"
    },
    {
      "line": 49,
      "text": "politic. p4"
    },
    {
      "line": 52,
      "text": "American/Soviet mission to Mars,"
    },
    {
      "line": 53,
      "text": "ip. 22"
    },
    {
      "line": 55,
      "text": "The World Information Economy,"
    },
    {
      "line": 56,
      "text": "p. 88"
    },
    {
      "line": 59,
      "text": "Electronic Privacy, p. 99"
    },
    {
      "line": 63,
      "text": "GC ciated |"
    },
    {
      "line": 69,
      "text": "This picture of AmerRuss’s flag ignited a controversy, See page |."
    },
    {
      "line": 73,
      "text": "David Jouris"
    },
    {
      "line": 76,
      "text": "ABOUT THE COVER"
    },
    {
      "line": 79,
      "text": "AMERRUSS IS THE COMBINED COUNTRY of America and Russia suggested by Robert Fuller"
    },
    {
      "line": 80,
      "text": "on page 30. In order to visualize this provocative idea and the internal conflicts it evokes, a flag"
    },
    {
      "line": 81,
      "text": "was in order. Photographer David Jouris and I worked out a design similar to the one displayed"
    },
    {
      "line": 82,
      "text": "below left. A week after our brainstorming, I happened to walk by the Flag Store in San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "line": 83,
      "text": "and was astounded to see that they sell the flags shown on the front cover as a stock off-the-shelf"
    },
    {
      "line": 84,
      "text": "item. We promptly rented three of them."
    },
    {
      "line": 87,
      "text": "This flag is one of two variations"
    },
    {
      "line": 88,
      "text": "on an American/Russian flag de-"
    },
    {
      "line": 89,
      "text": "signed at the Paramount Flag Co."
    },
    {
      "line": 90,
      "text": "They call it “USAR.” A different"
    },
    {
      "line": 91,
      "text": "joint flag, called “USSA,” has"
    },
    {
      "line": 93,
      "text": "a solid red field like the official"
    },
    {
      "line": 94,
      "text": "Soviet flag, but with 50 yellow"
    },
    {
      "line": 95,
      "text": "stars arrayed in the corner as in"
    },
    {
      "line": 96,
      "text": "the American flag. Both of these"
    },
